extends layout

block content
  h1 Macro Calculator For Cutting
  p 
    | This macro calculator is based *entirely* on the work of Mike Samuels at the 
    a(href='http://www.healthylivingheavylifting.com') Healthy Living, Heavy Lifting blog
    |  on the great post, 
    a(href="http://www.healthylivingheavylifting.com/how-to-calculate-macros-for-cutting/") How to Calculate Macros for Cutting
    | .
  
  br
  h3 Widget:
  #macro-calc
  script(type='text/javascript').
    !function(d,s,id,url){
      var js,fjs=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],p=/^http:/.test(d.location)?'http':'https';if(!d.getElementById(id)){js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;js.src=p+url;fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js,fjs);}
    }(document,'script','macro-calc-script', '://#{url}/widget.js');

  br
  br
  h3 Widget code:
  p Copy and paste this code where you want the widget to load.
  textarea#snippet
    #macro-calc
